{"word":"G3568 - νῦν - nŷn - noon - Henceforth","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νῦν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nŷn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">noon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Henceforth</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இப்பொழுது, இந்நேரம் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"now"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary particle of present time; &ldquo;now&rdquo; (as adverb of date, a transition or emphasis); also as noun or adjective <i>present</i> or <i>immediate</i>: - henceforth, + hereafter, of late, soon, present, this (time). See also <a href=\"#/G3569 - τανῦν - tanŷn - tan-oon'/3569\">G3569</a>, <a href=\"#/G3570 - νυνί - nyní - noo-nee'/3570\">G3570</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3568/3568\">G3568</a>, <a href=\"#/G3569/3569\">G3569</a>, <a href=\"#/G3570/3570\">G3570</a>"}]}